INSERT INTO `tb_noticias` VALUES (10,3,'mhgh','mhgh','kh kjh kjh kj h','<p>kajhsg dkfjha gskdjhfg</p>','uploads/noticias/captura_de_tela_2014-11-04_às_19.19.20.png',1,'2014-11-10 15:56:08','2014-11-10 15:56:08'),(11,4,'Teste','teste','teste 2','<p>asldf lajksd</p>','',1,'2014-11-10 16:30:48','2014-11-10 16:30:48'),(12,6,'Lorem Ipsum','lorem-ipsum','Marty, something has got to be done about your kids','<p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: \'Open Sans\', sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 21px; vertical-align: baseline; color: #444444;\">Say, why do you let those boys push you around like that? Thanks. Marty, one rejection isn\'t the end of the world. Then how am I supposed to ever meet anybody. Whoa, this is heavy.</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: \'Open Sans\', sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 21px; vertical-align: baseline; color: #444444;\">Ronald Reagon, the actor? Then who\'s vice president, Jerry Lewis? I suppose Jane Wymann is the first lady. Great good, good, Lorraine, I had a feeling about you two. Silence Earthling. my name is Darth Vader. I\'m am an extra-terrestrial from the planet Vulcan. Time machine, I haven\'t invented any time machine. I just wanna use the phone.</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: \'Open Sans\', sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 21px; vertical-align: baseline; color: #444444;\">You know Marty, you look so familiar, do I know your mother? Right, gimme a Pepsi free. Get out of town, I didn\'t know you did anything creative. Ah, let me read some. Kids, we\'re gonna have to eat this cake by ourselves, Uncle Joey didn\'t make parole again. I think it would be nice, if you all dropped him a line. No no no no no, Marty, both you and Jennifer turn out fine. It\'s your kids, Marty, something has got to be done about your kids.</p>','',1,'2014-11-10 16:58:58','2014-11-10 17:00:15');
